# Google Maps Platform API Key
# Used for the Geocoding API + Places API (New) — enrich each curated place
# with coordinates, ratings, hours, photos, and reviews.
# Get one at: https://console.cloud.google.com/ → APIs & Services → Credentials
# Required APIs (enable on the key): Geocoding API, Places API (New)
# Note: this is NOT the Maps JavaScript API — we use Mapbox for rendering.
NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=

# Mapbox Access Token (public, pk.* prefix)
# Used to render the map in the renderer (vector tiles, fonts, sprites).
# Get one at: https://account.mapbox.com/access-tokens/
# Strongly recommended: set a spending cap at https://account.mapbox.com/billing/
# so a viral share can never generate a surprise bill (free tier = 50k loads/mo).
NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN=
